Package: kitesurfdb
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight desktop database client for SQLite and PostgreSQL
 Kitesurf is a cross-platform desktop database client written in Rust
 using Dioxus. It supports SQLite and PostgreSQL with a tabbed interface,
 SQL editor with syntax highlighting, table browser, and schema introspection.
 .
 Features include saved connections with OS keyring password storage,
 light and dark themes, and low resource usage.
